The paper discusses the influence of values on the development and evaluation of machine learning models, which is a central topic in the field of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also touches on issues related to privacy and cybersecurity (cs.CY), as well as ethical considerations in the use of technology (cs.ET) and social implications of machine learning (cs.SI).
